    "Video Retrieval.",
    "Besides action recognition, we also conduct evaluations for the downstream video retrieval task on two human action datasets UCF101 and HMDB51.",
    "Table VIII shows the results of video retrieval of each method in terms of R@K, where R@K denotes the recall rate of top-K. All methods are pretrained on Kinetics-400 with the resolution of 112×112 for fair comparisons.",
    "The similar conclusion can be obtained that our CSVR achieves the best results on both UCF101 and HMDB51, showcasing its superiority for selfsupervised features learning for human action understanding.",
